column5: Gonna need a bigger boat. I have never seen such strange font on a news article, I thought I needed glasses. Now this story of catching a 14 metre 15 ton shark has to be true. I read it on the internet. The shark was thought to be extinct 28 to 1.5 million years ago. All of 28 years ago?
ultra fake news  It's not fake!!!!! They are not on the Left's list of fake news sites!!!!!
How did a story about finding a dead whale shark turn into this?  LOL!
